verbs.description: Blue states [V: are] defying the Trump administration in a bid to protect ObamaCare and keep their insurance markets stable . Several states , including California and Maryland , are looking to put limits on short - term insurance plans , even as the Trump administration is poised to expand access to them nationwide . The states are doing so because they fear the availability of the short - term plans will drive up premium costs for ObamaCare ....
